e structure remains sound.\n*   For the final display, I will use a flag to ensure the detailed mismatch display only runs once.\n\n**Constraint Check:** The golden testbench has `stimulus_gen` driving `a` and the DUTs receiving `a`. I must keep this structure. The new error display needs to be integrated while preserving the original statistical counting.",
